core":0,"quote":{"pid":"786f1e9bf6b390bc6ac20cfc077c02493bc32761","tid":877044,"uid":52590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都寫到故仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"有錢使得鬼推磨。<br />\n畀多啲錢，搵班人砌好個劇本就得。<br />\n至於有冇人睇，收視好唔好，根本唔係佢地考慮嘅範圍。<br />\n當拍廣告咁拍就得。"},{"pid":"748dc8b1c8de9b59fd49f5f9195279611eadc802","tid":877044,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7cbe861ee5d7de682815214bd6d349bb8efcc5","tid":877044,"uid":64191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"之前仲寫九七回歸，演員冇個香港人，又自詡香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"過多幾年。仲有人會care香港人？"},{"pid":"6d239929079446464a8f6232ccd3c3b9df1a4f63","tid":877044,"uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"應該係歲月風雲咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f14fdae68c833c31fca37ab44993f1911924ee","tid":877044,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"建橋偉業會唔會提死咗幾多人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b500ed14e68aa2003a591104704d5cf2cb869d6e","tid":877044,"uid":137814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"香港人對陸天明可能比較陌生，而其兒子陸川則曾執導《可可西里》、《南京！南京！》、<span style=\"color: red;\">《建黨偉業》等內地賣座電影</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284311034ea15e9dd8bd8574d5f6f18928c8159d","tid":877044,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74f14fdae68c833c31fca37ab44993f1911924ee","tid":877044,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"建橋偉業